---
title: Antares Programming
description: For Filipino web developers
permalink: /
---

<h1 class="sr-only">{{ title }}</h1>

<div class="padding--l cards-grid">
  {% for item in collections.posts | reverse %}
    {% set hasImage = loop.index0 % 4 === 0 %}
    <article class="card{{ " has-image" if hasImage }}">
      {% if hasImage %}
        <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="card__image" style="--bg-image: url({{ item.data.image }})"></a>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="card__body">
        <h2 class="card__title">
          <a class="card__link" href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
        <p>{{ item.data.description }}</p>
        <div class="spaced cluster">
          {% if item.data.author and authors[item.data.author] %}
            {% set author = authors[item.data.author] %}
            <a href="/authors/{{ item.data.author }}/" class="fg-theme-color card__link">{{ author.name }}</a>
          {% else %}
            <span class="weight-bold">Anonymous</span>
          {% endif %}
          <time datetime="{{ item.date | machineReadableDate }}">{{ item.date | humanReadableDate }}</time>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
<div class="cluster center-justified padding">
  <a href="/articles/" class="button secondary">Tingnan lahat</a>
</div>

<div class="newsletter">
  <form action="/newsletter/success" style="max-width: 65ch;" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="form 1">
    <div class="flex">
      <div class="form-contents">
        <h2 class="margin--none fs-2">Mag-subscribe sa aming newsletter</h2>
        <p class="margin--none">Maging updated sa mga bagong post, videos, at events ng Antares Programming</p>

        <div class="input-field">
          <label for="name" class="required">Pangalan</label>
          <input class="form-control" required="" placeholder="Halimbawa: Francis Rubio" id="name" name="name" type="text" inputmode="text" autocomplete="name">
        </div>

        <div class="input-field">
          <label for="email" class="required">Email address</label>
          <input class="form-control" required="" placeholder="Halimbawa: you@example.com" id="email" name="email" type="email" inputmode="email" autocomplete="email">
        </div>

        <div class="margin-inline--s">
          <button class="primary button touch margin-left--auto">Subscribe</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

<div class="padding--xxxl margin--auto" style="max-width: 100ch;">
  <h2>Tumatanggap kami ng donations!</h2>

  <p>Kung nakakatulong sa iyo ang content ng Antares Programming, puwede kang makatulong. Tumatanggap ang Antares Programming ng financial donations via GCash.</p>

  <div class="transparent bordered rounded box padding">
    <p>Sa GCash app, piliin ang <i>Send Money &gt; Express Send</i>. Ilagay ang number na ito, at ang amount na gusto mong i-donate.</p>

    <label for="gcash-number" class="sr-only">G-cash Number</label>
    <div class="form-group">
      <input value="0906 313 7462" class="form-control" type="text" readonly id="gcash-number">
      <button class="button secondary" data-copy="gcash-number">Copy</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>